window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Mary Jago had donated her own bone marrow to save the life of someone she didn’t know. And this generous act led directly to the bitter break-up of her affair with Alistair. For him, it was as though her beauty had been plundered.</p><p> But the man whose life she had saved would change Mary’s life in a way she could never have imagined.</p>"; 
